t offer services to other businesses \u2014 such as software companies, digital agencies, IT consultants, logistics firms, or HR solution providers \u2014 can use LinkedIn to reach procurement officers, finance directors, and operations managers in relevant industries.<\/p>\n<p class=\"\" data-start=\"740\" data-end=\"902\"><em data-start=\"740\" data-end=\"750\">Example:<\/em> A Kenyan SaaS company targeting HR managers in Nairobi\u2019s corporate sector can run LinkedIn campaigns filtered by company size, location, and job title.<\/p>\n<h3 class=\"\" data-start=\"909\" data-end=\"955\">2. <strong data-start=\"916\" data-end=\"955\">Training &amp; Educational Institutions<\/strong><\/h3>\n<p class=\"\" data-start=\"956\" data-end=\"1167\">Training companies, business schools, and universities offering executive education or corporate learning programmes can directly target HR and L&amp;D managers, school administrators, and directors of institutions.<\/p>\n<p class=\"\" data-start=\"1169\" data-end=\"1324\"><em data-start=\"1169\" data-end=\"1179\">Example:<\/em> A training firm offering ISO certification workshops can promote these to quality assurance managers in manufacturing and healthcare industries.<\/p>\n<h3 class=\"\" data-start=\"1331\" data-end=\"1369\">3. <strong data-start=\"1338\" data-end=\"1369\">Professional Services Firms<\/strong><\/h3>\n<p class=\"\" data-start=\"1370\" data-end=\"1582\">Law firms, tax consultants, architectural practices, and engineering consultancies that rely on professional credibility can use LinkedIn to showcase their expertise and win trust from high-level decision-makers.<\/p>\n<h3 class=\"\" data-start=\"1589\" data-end=\"1629\">4. <strong data-start=\"1596\" data-end=\"1629\">NGOs and Development Partners<\/strong><\/h3>\n<p class=\"\" data-start=\"1630\" data-end=\"1767\">Non-profits can use LinkedIn to promote programmes, raise awareness, recruit professionals, or engage with corporate partners and donors.<\/p>\n<p class=\"\" data-start=\"1769\" data-end=\"1929\"><em data-start=\"1769\" data-end=\"1779\">Example:<\/em> An NGO running an environmental sustainability programme can target CSR and ESG managers in Kenyan corporates and international development agencies.<\/p>\n<h3 class=\"\" data-start=\"1936\" data-end=\"1966\">5. <strong data-start=\"1943\" data-end=\"1966\">Corporate Employers<\/strong><\/h3>\n<p class=\"\" data-start=\"1967\" data-end=\"2140\">Companies hiring for senior or specialised roles can promote job listings directly to qualified professionals using sponsored job ads or content-based recruitment campaigns.<\/p>\n<h3 class=\"\" data-start=\"2147\" data-end=\"2197\">6. <strong data-start=\"2154\" data-end=\"2197\">Event Organisers &amp; B2B Conference Hosts<\/strong><\/h3>\n<p class=\"\" data-start=\"2198\" data-end=\"2342\">Promote summits, expos, networking forums or webinars directly to professionals who are most likely to attend, sponsor, or speak at your events.<\/p>\n<p>[\/vc_column_text][\/vc_column_inner][\/vc_row_inner][\/vc_column][\/vc_row][vc_row bg_type=&#8221;bg_color&#8221;][vc_column][vc_cta h2=&#8221;Wondering if LinkedIn Ads are right for your industry?&#8221; h2_font_container=&#8221;tag:h2|text_align:left|color:%23000000&#8243; h2_use_theme_fonts=&#8221;yes&#8221; h2_css_animation=&#8221;fadeInLeft&#8221; h4_font_container=&#8221;tag:h4|text_align:left|color:%230A0A0A&#8221; h4_use_theme_fonts=&#8221;yes&#8221; shape=&#8221;square&#8221; style=&#8221;flat&#8221; color=&#8221;grey&#8221; add_button=&#8221;right&#8221; btn_title=&#8221;Contact Us&#8221; btn_shape=&#8221;square&#8221; btn_color=&#8221;warning&#8221; btn_i_align=&#8221;right&#8221; btn_i_icon_fontawesome=&#8221;fa fa-solid fa-paper-plane&#8221; btn_css_animation=&#8221;bounceIn&#8221; css=&#8221;&#8221; use_custom_fonts_h2=&#8221;true&#8221; use_custom_fonts_h4=&#8221;true&#8221; btn_add_icon=&#8221;true&#8221; btn_link=&#8221;url:%23!%2Fcontact&#8221;]Speak to our experts![