 testing of content variations<\/p>\n<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<h3 class=\"\" data-start=\"950\" data-end=\"1013\">2. <strong data-start=\"957\" data-end=\"1013\">Sponsored Messaging (Message Ads &amp; Conversation Ads)<\/strong><\/h3>\n<p class=\"\" data-start=\"1014\" data-end=\"1186\">These ads land directly in a user\u2019s LinkedIn inbox. They create a personal connection and are perfect for invitations to events, direct lead generation, or tailored offers.<\/p>\n<p class=\"\" data-start=\"1188\" data-end=\"1287\"><strong data-start=\"1188\" data-end=\"1201\">Use Case:<\/strong> Send personalised invites to procurement heads for an industry event or product demo.<\/p>\n<p class=\"\" data-start=\"1289\" data-end=\"1302\"><strong data-start=\"1289\" data-end=\"1302\">Includes:<\/strong><\/p>\n<ul data-start=\"1303\" data-end=\"1435\">\n<li class=\"\" data-start=\"1303\" data-end=\"1355\">\n<p class=\"\" data-start=\"1305\" data-end=\"1355\">Custom sender name (e.g. \u201cFaith from amini Digital\u201d)<\/p>\n<\/li>\n<li class=\"\" data-start=\"1356\" data-end=\"1399\">\n<p class=\"\" data-start=\"1358\" data-end=\"1399\">Message sequencing (for Conversation Ads)<\/p>\n<\/li>\n<li class=\"\" data-start=\"1400\" data-end=\"1435\">\n<p class=\"\" data-start=\"1402\" data-end=\"1435\">Lead forms or link click tracking<\/p>\n<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<h3 class=\"\" data-start=\"1442\" data-end=\"1470\">3. <strong data-start=\"1449\" data-end=\"1470\">Lead Gen Form Ads<\/strong><\/h3>\n<p class=\"\" data-start=\"1471\" data-end=\"1666\">Lead Gen Form Ads combine sponsored content or message ads with a native form pre-filled with LinkedIn profile data. This makes it easy for users to submit their details without leaving LinkedIn.<\/p>\n<p class=\"\" data-start=\"1668\" data-end=\"1753\"><strong data-start=\"1668\" data-end=\"1681\">Use Case:<\/strong> Capture leads for a free consultation, audit, or downloadable resource.<\/p>\n<p class=\"\" data-start=\"1755\" data-end=\"1768\"><strong data-start=\"1755\" data-end=\"1768\">Includes:<\/strong><\/p>\n<ul data-start=\"1769\" data-end=\"1903\">\n<li class=\"\" data-start=\"1769\" data-end=\"1828\">\n<p class=\"\" data-start=\"1771\" data-end=\"1828\">Custom form fields (e.g. name, email, company, job title)<\/p>\n<\/li>\n<li class=\"\" data-start=\"1829\" data-end=\"1859\">\n<p class=\"\" data-start=\"1831\" data-end=\"1859\">Automated thank-you messages<\/p>\n<\/li>\n<li class=\"\" data-start=\"1860\" data-end=\"1903\">\n<p class=\"\" data-start=\"1862\" data-end=\"1903\">Integration with your CRM or email system<\/p>\n<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<h3 class=\"\" data-start=\"1910\" data-end=\"1929\">4. <strong data-start=\"1917\" data-end=\"1929\">Text Ads<\/strong><\/h3>\n<p class=\"\" data-start=\"1930\" data-end=\"2117\">These appear on the right-hand side of the LinkedIn desktop interface. They\u2019re simple, cost-effective, and good for driving traffic or brand awareness among a broad professional audience.<\/p>\n<p class=\"\" data-start=\"2119\" data-end=\"2201\"><strong data-start=\"2119\" data-end=\"2132\">Use Case:<\/strong> Drive clicks to a landing page promoting corporate training courses.<\/p>\n<h3 class=\"\" data-start=\"2208\" data-end=\"2230\">5. <strong data-start=\"2215\" data-end=\"2230\">Dynamic Ads<\/strong><\/h3>\n<p class=\"\" data-start=\"2231\" data-end=\"2426\">These are automatically personalised to each user, showing their profile picture, name, or company within the ad. They\u2019re useful for driving follower growth, content downloads, or event sign-ups.<\/p>\n<p class=\"\" data-start=\"2428\" data-end=\"2552\"><strong data-start=\"2428\" data-end=\"2441\">Use Case:<\/strong> Increase your LinkedIn Page followers among Kenyan business executives or promote your latest industry report.<\/p>\n<h3 class=\"\" data-start=\"2559\" data-end=\"2579\">6. <strong data-start=\"2566\" data-end=\"2579\">Event Ads<\/strong><\/h3>\n<p class=\"\" data-start=\"2580\" data-end=\"2738\">These are tailored specifically for promoting LinkedIn Events. They allow you to reach relevant professionals and track engagement directly from the platform.<\/p>\n<p class=\"\" data-start=\"2740\" data-end=\"2829\"><strong data-start=\"2740\" data-end=\"2753\">Use Case:<\/strong> Promote an upcoming webinar on compliance or an invite-only CEO roundtable.<\/p>\n<p>[\/vc_column_text][\/vc_column_inner][\/vc_row_inner][\/vc_column][\/vc_row][vc_row][vc_column][vc_row_inner][vc_column_inner][vc_column_text css=&#8221;&#8221;]<\/p>\n<h2 class=\"\" data-start=\"0\" data-end=\"57\">Why Choose amini Digital Agency for LinkedIn Advertising<\/h2>\n<p class=\"\" data-start=\"59\" data-end=\"301\">LinkedIn advertising is not about guesswork \u2014 it\u2019s about strategy, data, and execution. At amini Digital Agency, we help Kenyan organisations cut through the noise and run performance-driven LinkedIn campaigns that generate real business leads.<\/p>\n<p class=\"\" data-start=\"303\" data-end=\"423\">Here\u2019s why we are the preferred LinkedIn ad agency for B2B brands, corporates, NGOs, and training institutions in Kenya:<\/p>\n<h3 class=\"\" data-start=\"430\" data-end=\"462\">1. <strong data-start=\"437\" data-end=\"462\">B2B-Focused Expertise<\/strong><\/h3>\n<p class=\"\" data-start=\"463\" data-end=\"712\">Unlike generalist digital agencies, we specialise in B2B advertising. Our team understands the complexity of B2B buying cycles, multi-stakeholder decision-making, and high-value lead nurturing \u2014 making our strategies more aligned to your objectives.<\/p>\n<p class=\"\" data-start=\"714\" data-end=\"837\"><em data-start=\"714\" data-end=\"837\">Whether you\u2019re targeting Heads of Procurement, L&amp;D Managers, or Finance Directors, we know how to reach them effectively.<\/em><\/p>\n<h3 class=\"\" data-start=\"844\" data-end=\"889\">2. <strong data-start=\"851\" data-end=\"889\">Certified LinkedIn Ads Specialists<\/strong><\/h3>\n<p class=\"\" data-start=\"890\" data-end=\"1